@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@contentType = application/json
@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.data.token}}
@userToken = {{loginUser.response.body.data.token}}

### Prerequisites: Run auth.rest first to get tokens

### 1. Create a Category (Positive Case - Admin)
# @name createCategory
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Skincare
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

All kinds of skincare products
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="skincare.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./skincare.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Capture created category ID
@categoryId = {{createCategory.response.body.data._id}}

### 2. Get All Categories (Positive Case - Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### 3. Update Category (Positive Case - Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Skincare Updated
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Updated description for skincare
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 4. Create Category (Negative Case - Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Unauthorized Category"
}

### 5. Create Category (Negative Case - Forbidden - Normal User)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Forbidden Category"
}

### 6. Create Category with Invalid Data (Negative Case - 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "S",
  "description": "Too short name"
}

### 7. Delete Category (Positive Case - Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. Delete Category (Negative Case - Not Found - 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
